 some joy.<br>
<br>
It happens to be that the neutrals have aquired some new allies in their fight. Darkenbane Company has joined Sullen Zek and is on the neutral team. That's right all you DB haters, they are back, and they are on your team. The guild most often accused of cheating, foul play, exploiting, and cheesy tactics is back, and without any of those rules haha.<br>
<br>
I just find it funny that most of those people who hated DB all that time have to just learn to live with them, and Rely on them in battle. Of course this isnt too surprising being that most of the uber groups that shunned the guild secretly had little twinkies that ran around and did all those foul things to thier supposed friends. <br>
<br>
-Anni <p>Stalker Of Sullen Zek.</p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#3B3B3B><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub13.ezboard.com/umajestykvz.showPublicProfile?language=EN>MajestykVZ</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Registered User</span><br> <font color=#FF0000>(7/7/01 8:06:08 am)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub35.ezboard.com/fthesafehousefrm15.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=400.topic&index=1>Reply</a>   </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re: SZ Neutrals.</span><hr size=1> Who? <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#2f2f4f><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub13.ezboard.com/ukambic.showPublicProfile?language=EN>Kambic</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Registered User</span><br> <font color=#FF0000>(7/7/01 9:57:47 am)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub35.ezboard.com/fthesafehousefrm15.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=400.topic&index=2>Reply</a>   <BR><img src=http://members.theglobe.com/Kambic/TRINITY.GIF WIDTH=60 HEIGHT=60></td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re: SZ Neutrals.</span><hr size=1> A guild from Rallos.<br>
<br>
