"Aww, but I'm mad <i>now</i>." - Homer Simpson, buying a gun</p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#3B3B3B><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub13.ezboard.com/uannid.showPublicProfile?language=EN>Anni D</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Registered User</span><br> <font color=#FF0000>(7/7/01 8:58:04 pm)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub35.ezboard.com/fthesafehousefrm15.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=400.topic&index=3>Reply</a>   </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re: SZ Neutrals.</span><hr size=1> Do not misunderstand. I thought I was clear that they were accused the most. Not that they actually did.<br>
<br>
Darkenbane as a guild has a tendancy to be classified as cheaters. Granted, they do have more than their share of them, but that is only because of the types of players which are drawn to the kill everyone and get their ph4t l3wt mindset.<br>
<br>
The guild also has a lot of solid pvp players, although most of them on rallos left the guild because the idiots were invading. It will be interesting to see how it all comes out in the end.<br>
<br>
Many goodies are considering leaving, and of course their main choice is evil because of the iksars getting so high so fast. I wish all zones had newbie quests that were like.. umm.. useful.<br>
<br>
-Anni <p>Stalker Of Sullen Zek.</p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#2f2f4f><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub13.ezboard.com/umordier.showPublicProfile?language=EN>Mordier</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Registered User</span><br> <font color=#FF0000>(7/8/01 7:03:22 am)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub35.ezboard.com/fthesafehousefrm15.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=400.topic&index=4>Reply</a>   </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re: SZ Neutrals.</span><hr size=1> Don't know the guild, but do everyone a favor, be a class act.  I'd love to see more good guilds from other servers start a branch on Vallon, but some of these groups coming over seem to only want to play to grief.  <br>
<br>
Be a class act. <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#3B3B3B><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub13.ezboard.com/ukambic.showPublicProfile?language=EN>Kambic</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Registered User</span><br> <font color=#FF0000>(7/9/01 8:07:40 am)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub35.ezboard.com/fthesafehousefrm15.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=400.topic&index=5>Reply</a>   <BR><img src=http://members.theglobe.com/Kambic/TRINITY.GIF WIDTH=60 HEIGHT=60></td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re: SZ Neutrals.</span><hr size=1> "Many goodies are considering leaving, and of course their main choice is evil because of the iksars getting so high so fast. I wish all zones had newbie quests that were like.. umm.. useful."<br>
